race.description: Express Smash Repairs Midway Conditional Hcp (Bm68)
race.comment: YOUR NOT THE BOSS (11) solid gelding who will find this more to his liking third-up. Looks to have a good win in him this campaign after closing late when seventh over 1200m at Moruya. Ready for this trip and further now and no excuses today. TARTANA (5) sound return from back in the field when a tidy second over 1200m at Moruya. Has a decent second-up record and proven in the going. LOS PADRES (1) comes to hand quickly and will relish the extra trip second-up. Closed strongly from last on the turn with a close-up fourth over 1200m at this track. Key jockey change and must be kept safe. KIRKUK (8) holding his form and looks well placed today with the 4kg claim. Gripped on late when a fighting second over 1400m at this track. Hard fit and not to be overlooked.
